short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Track packages on a easy and organized way

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Tracking Extension is a practical and efficient tool for tracking your packages directly in your browser. Designed to offer a simple and intuitive tracking experience, it allows you to easily monitor the status of your deliveries.

Obs: To work in a location other than Brazil, an API change is required.
